        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Ok Nyxx..?</P><P>1).  Yes, we're the parent class.  I'll agree to disagree on this one, we *should* have it.<BR>3).  I beg to differ, we are "Masters" of the undead.  Though I'd agree that it would overpower us if they gave us an undead-mezz line, but are you going to spend your hard earned points for a 72 minute refresh AE undead only mezz?<BR>5).  I know how to use those spells just fine and I do all day; but why should we have to give away our hp to our pets when we used to not have to?<BR>6).  The AE thing is more of a fun option ;)<BR>8).  Our epic stats are fucking lame compared to others.  That on top of the graphic...<BR>12).  Do you keep Levant memmed for escape?  Or for travel?...  I've never once kept it memmed to get outta trouble - Why?  Because it's night only and you can't count on getting in trouble between 8pm and 5am; hence FD has that spell slot.  So, yes, our Levant shouldn't reload the zone.<BR>14).  Ok I'll bite, when the fuck did we get Group DMF?<BR>17).  What's so funny about not being able to fix Venril Sathir faction?  Goods can fix FV faction easily (albeit slowly).  My faction with them is fine, so I'm not complaining on my behalf.  It's just a fact.<BR>18).  "Magic"? lol.  Whatever.  Maybe if "magic" loosely translates into "A lazy way for Verant to curtail our power".</P><P>You sound like a new necro; like one of the clarity-huggers of the new generation.  My only point was that any number of these things are far more important that boosting the power of our pets; as they work as intended.</P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
