        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">To Jeddia:</P><P>1) I agree... Death Peace SHOULD be ours, not cause SK's have it but because we NEED it. With the Death Peace skill in SoL SK's won't even have to mem the spell.</P><P>3) I just want an upgrade to ST. Even if it is just 0.5 secs faster and lasts only 5 secs longer. Just gimme that ST upgrade!</P><P>5) Yeah. Better pet heal would be nice.</P><P>8) Do you have the epic? Have you compared it to others? It averages to same stats. hp+mana on epics = 100. Saves averages to 10sv all on epics. 20int while others have 20wis etc. Average stats on all epics and they are the same! The effect on Necro epic is great too - every necro I know would love to trade their Z-heart for epic if they could. And I for sure love my duckstaff. </P><P>14) We got group DMF some 2 months ago... back when they first revamped Chardok. I thought every necro knew this? FYI it is level 49 spell and costs 375 mana.</P><P>17) I agree with you on the VS faction... many of our 50+ spells are sold there exclusively, but a couple nights in HS or Karnors screws your faction there. Silly.</P><P>18) agree here also. Just like PoG where the plants are "summoned" like VI stated and not plants. WTF!? No plants on Plane of GROWTH? Why did they bother making the spell at all.</P><P><font size=-2>Sick with suffering. The stench and filth of him. Death all around him. The flies, the dogs, the din. King of death and pain. Ruler of the slain. Bleak horror. His kingdom of the ghost. <b>.Vermis.Mysteriis.Defiler.<BR></b><BR></font></P><P>Edited by - Vermis Mysteriis on 12/15/2001  05:54:47<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
