        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Most of those things you said you wanted change are out of the question.</P><P>As much as I would like aoes, even undead only aoes, it will never happen.</P><P>I would so love to be able to go into HS aoe groups more often then I can as a necro,but it will not happen with our class.  Wer'e not gizzards.</P><P>I agree with necros getting death peace.  I can think of no other spell that the 'parent class' gets before the subordinate, with the subordinate getting an exclusive upgrade that is just an improved version of the spell.</P><P>Infusion reagent needs to stay where it is, if you make it a buyable item, its just going to make you spend more plat to use it.  As it is now, you probably have infusion on page 50 of yourspell book, and thats fine.  Lots of classes have useless spells.</P><P>Our pet heal line is fabulous, what are you talking about?  Magicians envy us in this department.</P><P>The things that need to be changed are this:</P><P>Fix qvoz to overwrite, or stack with all lich forms.  </P><P>Allow spectre pet to use weapons.</P><P>Give us a better mana spell in the lich line, or a self only shield with built in mana regen. And no, I'm not talking manaskin.  In kunark we regenned mana at a MUCH faster rate then any other class.  Now druids get potg, wizards get familiars, shaman get canniblize 4, etc etc etc.  Our mana regeneration rate is not that much higher then a lot of other classes now, and thats an issue.  We get shafted on the mana for damage ratio compared to other classes.  Perhaps a shield spell like shield of the magi, where instead of MR, it gives mana regen.  Make it level 57 or so, and have it be the same mana regen as potg (but the spell would not stack with potg)  </P><P><BR><img src="http://www.users.qwest.net/~morbid909/ezboardsig.jpg" border=0><br>Those who have turned away, shall be turned upon.<BR> <br>Ravanta Suffer 60 DE Necro Innoruuk <img src=icon_smile_evil.gif b