        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">As far as the Death Peace thing goes..yes. I think Necros should have gotten this as well. It fits both roleplay and logical reasoning that we should get it. </P><P>What would you say if suddenly SKs were given a summon corpse upgrade that summoned two corpses or the corpse of everyone in the group? Be kinda wrong dont ya think? From a RP standpoint, Necros researched the spell, we perfected it and used it long before SKs did. It would only make sense that a Necro would come across a more improved version of the spell...and even if SKs did infact find it before Necros, it wouldnt remain a secret to Necros for long. So yes...we should have this spell.</P><P><img src="http://www.netset.com/~blazer/mem1.jpg" border=0><img src="http://www.netset.com/~blazer/sig6.jpg" border=0></P><P><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
